1
00:00:00,970 --> 00:00:03,640
(Episode 95)

2
00:00:05,240 --> 00:00:06,440
Keep an eye on me?

3
00:00:07,010 --> 00:00:09,710
Shit. Do you think
I'll let you get your way?

4
00:00:10,680 --> 00:00:12,550
I'll give you some time for now.

5
00:00:13,080 --> 00:00:16,390
But you will pay dearly
for the crimes you've committed.

6
00:00:18,120 --> 00:00:20,530
(Suk Hee's Side Dishes)

7
00:00:22,730 --> 00:00:24,130
You're so pretty, Jang Mi.

8
00:00:25,100 --> 00:00:26,800
My wonderful Jang Mi.

9
00:00:27,900 --> 00:00:29,930
Jang Mi is Suk Hee's daughter.

10
00:00:31,240 --> 00:00:33,040
My Jang Mi is so pretty.

11
00:00:35,610 --> 00:00:37,610
I love how you smell, Mom.

12
00:00:45,150 --> 00:00:47,050
Running off with the bride and everything.

13
00:00:47,190 --> 00:00:48,890
I'm impressed, Kang Baek Ho.

14
00:00:49,390 --> 00:00:50,390
Come on.

15
00:01:04,440 --> 00:01:07,410
If you so much as breathe a word
about the twins to Father,

16
00:01:07,770 --> 00:01:10,210
I'll leak the photos of your affair.

17
00:01:10,340 --> 00:01:11,480
The choice is yours, Yeom San Wol.

18
00:01:11,580 --> 00:01:13,410
Alright, I got it.

19
00:01:13,410 --> 00:01:16,450
I won't say a thing about the twins,
so don't worry.

20
00:01:18,020 --> 00:01:19,850
The Chairman is coming. I have to go.

21
00:01:24,960 --> 00:01:26,360
Darling.

22
00:01:26,930 --> 00:01:28,290
You must have been so shocked.

23
00:01:28,290 --> 00:01:30,730
Why are you home, Mrs. Yeom?

24
00:01:31,100 --> 00:01:33,300
Did you know the wedding was going
to fall apart?

25
00:01:33,360 --> 00:01:35,170
No, of course not.

26
00:01:37,040 --> 00:01:40,670
Why did Seo Rin collapse?

27
00:01:41,170 --> 00:01:42,310
What?

28
00:01:42,310 --> 00:01:44,180
Seo Rin collapsed?

29
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:47,680
I don't really know...

30
00:01:50,650 --> 00:01:52,080
Darling...

31
00:01:55,150 --> 00:01:56,320
I'm so sorry, Father.

32
00:01:57,020 --> 00:02:00,960
I think Seo Rin was too stressed
from planning the wedding.

33
00:02:01,130 --> 00:02:03,960
- Where is Seo Rin?
- She just fainted for a moment.

34
00:02:04,800 --> 00:02:06,500
I'm just on my way back
from admitting her to the hospital.

35
00:02:06,700 --> 00:02:08,600
She still needs to rest?

36
00:02:08,870 --> 00:02:10,370
And is she conscious?

37
00:02:10,440 --> 00:02:13,140
Yes, you don't need to worry.

38
00:02:13,540 --> 00:02:16,710
I'll bring her home as soon as
she's calmed down from the IV.

39
00:02:17,340 --> 00:02:20,480
She needs her rest right now,
so no visitors are allowed.

40
00:02:21,150 --> 00:02:24,050
- I'm sorry.
- You have nothing to be sorry for.

41
00:02:24,780 --> 00:02:28,320
My poor baby was just too stressed out
over the wedding.

42
00:02:28,820 --> 00:02:31,790
She's never had a stressful day,

43
00:02:31,920 --> 00:02:33,190
so she just got overwhelmed.

44
00:02:33,460 --> 00:02:35,460
Yes, I think that must be it, Father.

45
00:02:48,340 --> 00:02:50,580
- Secretary Kim.
- Yes, Chairman.

46
00:02:50,580 --> 00:02:54,010
It looks like there was some commotion
at the wedding today.

47
00:02:54,580 --> 00:02:56,650
Find out what happened.

48
00:02:57,220 --> 00:03:00,080
And find out why Seo Rin collapsed.

49
00:03:15,030 --> 00:03:16,030
Okay.

50
00:03:17,340 --> 00:03:19,300
You can't get in touch
with Ssangkal's girlfriend?

51
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:22,570
- Don't tell me, CEO Chae...
- I'm afraid so.

52
00:03:23,880 --> 00:03:25,410
I really hope we can reach her.

53
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:30,380
What are we going to do now
that Seo Rin is in CEO Chae's clutches?

54
00:03:30,620 --> 00:03:32,220
We have to find Seo Rin quickly.

55
00:03:32,550 --> 00:03:36,150
- I know where she was being kept.
- You do?

56
00:03:36,220 --> 00:03:40,260
I couldn't meet her because
she'd already escaped before I got there,

57
00:03:40,390 --> 00:03:41,790
but I'm positive that's where she was.

58
00:03:41,930 --> 00:03:44,230
Before Chae Hwa Young does something
to her,

59
00:03:44,530 --> 00:03:46,060
we have to get her out of there fast.

60
00:03:47,630 --> 00:03:49,470
It's Ms. Geum Soon.

61
00:03:50,100 --> 00:03:52,370
Answer it. Ask if Seo Rin is home.

62
00:03:53,570 --> 00:03:54,710
Yes, Ms. Geum Soon?

63
00:03:55,210 --> 00:03:56,540
Is Seo Rin home?

64
00:03:56,770 --> 00:04:00,210
CEO Chae says that Seo Rin fainted.

65
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:04,320
She told the Chairman she's hospitalized,
and no one's allowed to visit.

66
00:04:04,450 --> 00:04:07,390
Chae Hwa Young
is up to her old tricks again.

67
00:04:07,450 --> 00:04:10,150
I guess it's the best she could do
under the circumstances.

68
00:04:10,460 --> 00:04:12,260
It's not like she can explain
the situation about you and Seo Rin.

69
00:04:13,090 --> 00:04:15,930
It looks like she's making sure
Mrs. Yeom keeps her mouth shut, too.

70
00:04:18,960 --> 00:04:21,000
You just try running your mouth
in front of Father.

71
00:04:21,330 --> 00:04:24,200
I'll plaster your affair photos
all over the world.

72
00:04:24,270 --> 00:04:27,070
That's why I'm keeping my mouth shut!

73
00:04:27,140 --> 00:04:29,140
Stop anyone who comes to see Father.

74
00:04:29,540 --> 00:04:31,540
Don't even let a fly in.

75
00:04:31,540 --> 00:04:33,710
Who specifically?

76
00:04:33,780 --> 00:04:37,350
I don't want to see Oh Jang Mi,
Kang Baek Ho, or anyone else.

77
00:04:37,580 --> 00:04:40,350
But do you really think we can stop them?

78
00:04:40,420 --> 00:04:42,120
That's not your problem.

79
00:04:42,490 --> 00:04:45,520
You two just do what I say. Understood?

80
00:04:46,260 --> 00:04:48,460
Don't you forget it,
Yeom San Wol and Jin Hong Ju.

81
00:05:01,210 --> 00:05:02,310
My heart is racing.

82
00:05:02,610 --> 00:05:04,910
That witch just gets more vicious
every day.

83
00:05:05,740 --> 00:05:08,810
Mom, are you sure
it was really Seo Rin who came home?

84
00:05:08,910 --> 00:05:10,450
I told you it was.

85
00:05:10,650 --> 00:05:13,920
She yelled, "What do you mean, a wedding?
I'm right here!"

86
00:05:14,090 --> 00:05:17,320
Then she stormed out, screaming,
"Shit! Shit!"

87
00:05:18,060 --> 00:05:19,790
Now that I think about it,

88
00:05:20,260 --> 00:05:22,230
it's been a while
since I've heard her say "Shit."

89
00:05:23,530 --> 00:05:27,670
So that means Oh Jang Mi was pretending
to be Ma Seo Rin this whole time.

90
00:05:27,770 --> 00:05:30,330
She's been fooling us completely
this whole time?

91
00:05:31,740 --> 00:05:32,870
No wonder.

92
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:35,470
I always thought it was strange,

93
00:05:35,470 --> 00:05:37,110
the way Baek Ho looked longingly
at Director Ma.

94
00:05:38,380 --> 00:05:40,510
That's it. That's what was going on.

95
00:05:41,580 --> 00:05:43,010
So annoying.

96
00:05:43,580 --> 00:05:47,020
That Oh Jang Mi always finds a way
to ruin my life.

97
00:05:47,520 --> 00:05:49,550
Oh Jang Mi? It's me.

98
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:51,920
Goodness!

99
00:05:55,030 --> 00:05:57,760
- Give it to me! Give it to me now!
- No, I can't!

100
00:05:58,100 --> 00:06:00,700
I was told to watch you closely.
I'll get fired if this happens.

101
00:06:00,770 --> 00:06:04,300
Shit. Do you have any idea who I am?
Give it back!

102
00:06:04,370 --> 00:06:05,570
Ma Seo Rin! Seo Rin...

103
00:06:06,870 --> 00:06:08,070
The line went dead.

104
00:06:09,640 --> 00:06:12,480
The phone you are calling is turned off.
You will be transferred to voicemail...

105
00:06:14,150 --> 00:06:15,480
Her phone's already off.

106
00:06:26,260 --> 00:06:27,690
I just can't believe this.

107
00:06:28,390 --> 00:06:29,590
Good grief.

108
00:06:29,930 --> 00:06:32,400
In all my years,
I've never seen such a mess.

109
00:06:35,430 --> 00:06:36,700
You're happy, aren't you?

110
00:06:37,670 --> 00:06:39,970
Since Jun Ho and Director Ma's wedding
was called off,

111
00:06:40,300 --> 00:06:43,140
you must be thrilled inside, right?

112
00:06:43,270 --> 00:06:44,310
What?

113
00:06:44,410 --> 00:06:46,710
At the thought you might have a chance
with Chae Hwa Young now,

114
00:06:47,110 --> 00:06:48,980
you must be over the moon, right?

115
00:06:49,710 --> 00:06:51,480
Stop being ridiculous.

116
00:06:51,620 --> 00:06:53,280
What did I do now?

117
00:06:54,320 --> 00:06:55,420
Where do you think you're going?

118
00:06:56,090 --> 00:06:57,290
Don't run away
and listen to what I have to say.

119
00:06:58,120 --> 00:06:59,920
What do you want from me?

120
00:06:59,990 --> 00:07:02,630
I want you to beg and plead
until I'm not angry anymore.

121
00:07:03,830 --> 00:07:06,630
But even then, I'll never forgive you.

122
00:07:06,630 --> 00:07:07,870
Who said I'm asking for forgiveness?

123
00:07:08,870 --> 00:07:10,570
I'm not going to beg for your forgiveness.

124
00:07:11,970 --> 00:07:14,540
Still insisting you did nothing wrong,
right to the very end.

125
00:07:14,940 --> 00:07:17,710
That's what makes me even more furious.
Don't you get it?

126
00:07:17,780 --> 00:07:19,480
What did I do that was so wrong?

127
00:07:19,980 --> 00:07:22,910
I followed my heart with no regrets.

128
00:07:22,910 --> 00:07:24,180
Hey! Kang Nam Bong!

129
00:07:24,250 --> 00:07:27,320
It was a new experience,
feeling that excitement so late in life.

130
00:07:27,690 --> 00:07:30,350
I was grateful to her
for making me feel alive.

131
00:07:30,690 --> 00:07:31,990
What did you just say?

132
00:07:32,690 --> 00:07:33,720
Why you!

133
00:07:34,130 --> 00:07:37,930
Hey! You were grateful?
You were grateful to that tramp?

134
00:07:38,200 --> 00:07:40,870
Were your feelings all that mattered?

135
00:07:40,870 --> 00:07:42,130
Let me go!

136
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:46,440
Don't expect me to apologize.

137
00:07:46,440 --> 00:07:48,570
- Hey!
- It's over with Chae Hwa Young.

138
00:07:49,140 --> 00:07:51,240
Even if you told me
to see her again, I wouldn't.

139
00:07:51,710 --> 00:07:54,210
So just drop it already!

140
00:07:58,620 --> 00:08:00,480
All you care about is yourself!
You're so selfish!

141
00:08:01,120 --> 00:08:02,750
Are you saying only your feelings matter,

142
00:08:02,750 --> 00:08:05,490
and you don't care what happens to me?

143
00:08:09,930 --> 00:08:11,130
That's not true, Father.

144
00:08:11,700 --> 00:08:13,970
He's been pursuing me this whole time.

145
00:08:14,900 --> 00:08:17,300
He saw me as a widow
and then targeted and stalked me.

146
00:08:17,300 --> 00:08:18,870
That's why we're in this mess, Father.

147
00:08:26,340 --> 00:08:27,350
Hwa Young.

148
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:29,680
Was I...

149
00:08:30,620 --> 00:08:31,750
a stalker to you?

150
00:08:33,280 --> 00:08:34,490
Just a stalker?

151
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:37,860
How could you say that?

152
00:08:39,460 --> 00:08:40,490
How could you?

153
00:08:46,500 --> 00:08:48,200
It's hot. Careful.

154
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:56,840
Jun Ho.

155
00:08:57,610 --> 00:08:58,740
What are you doing here?

156
00:08:59,340 --> 00:09:01,610
- I need to talk to you.
- You have nothing to talk about.

157
00:09:02,950 --> 00:09:04,850
- Talk to me, Jun Ho.
- Baek Ho.

158
00:09:05,420 --> 00:09:08,320
I'm the one who started this,
so I'll be the one to end it.

159
00:09:17,260 --> 00:09:18,460
I'm sorry, Jun Ho.

160
00:09:19,060 --> 00:09:21,330
The wedding was called off,
but we can just reschedule...

161
00:09:21,400 --> 00:09:22,530
But you know...

162
00:09:23,370 --> 00:09:25,740
- that Seo Rin is back.
- That doesn't matter...

163
00:09:26,540 --> 00:09:28,370
because you're the one I love, Jang Mi.

164
00:09:28,440 --> 00:09:30,810
All this was that
I needed you as Ma Seo Rin,

165
00:09:31,410 --> 00:09:33,280
and you needed me to be her...

166
00:09:33,680 --> 00:09:36,180
so you could get into the Dream family.

167
00:09:37,210 --> 00:09:38,220
No.

168
00:09:38,950 --> 00:09:41,150
I'm in love with you,
Jang Mi, not Ma Seo Rin.

169
00:09:42,020 --> 00:09:45,890
I don't need Dream family or CEO Chae.

170
00:09:46,520 --> 00:09:48,260
All I need is you.

171
00:09:48,430 --> 00:09:51,060
But Seo Rin is in love with you.

172
00:09:51,730 --> 00:09:53,360
And I used you,

173
00:09:53,900 --> 00:09:55,330
the one my sister loves,

174
00:09:56,100 --> 00:09:57,100
and for that alone,

175
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:59,370
I feel so guilty toward Seo Rin
that I could die.

176
00:10:00,470 --> 00:10:01,470
Then what about me?

177
00:10:04,010 --> 00:10:05,010
What am I to you?

178
00:10:05,940 --> 00:10:06,940
I'm sorry.

179
00:10:08,450 --> 00:10:10,950
I know I told you to try and make me
fall in love with you,

180
00:10:12,380 --> 00:10:14,590
but that was an impossible mission
from the start.

181
00:10:16,120 --> 00:10:17,890
And now that Seo Rin is back,

182
00:10:18,490 --> 00:10:20,260
I have to protect her feelings for you.

183
00:10:20,890 --> 00:10:21,890
So...

184
00:10:22,630 --> 00:10:23,760
please just let this go.

185
00:10:29,170 --> 00:10:30,170
I love you.

186
00:10:32,200 --> 00:10:33,200
Please, just choose me.

187
00:10:33,900 --> 00:10:35,070
I'll handle everything else.

188
00:10:36,640 --> 00:10:38,380
The only reason I chose you...

189
00:10:40,080 --> 00:10:41,910
is that I'm in love with Baek Ho.

190
00:10:43,750 --> 00:10:45,280
I didn't want to have to say this,

191
00:10:46,350 --> 00:10:47,350
but I agreed to that marriage...

192
00:10:48,390 --> 00:10:49,590
to protect Baek Ho...

193
00:10:50,190 --> 00:10:52,320
from Chae Hwa Young.

194
00:10:53,660 --> 00:10:57,030
As long as I could save Baek Ho,
I didn't care what happened to me.

195
00:10:57,830 --> 00:10:59,460
Even if it meant living with you
as an empty shell.

196
00:11:00,300 --> 00:11:02,870
- As long as my Baek Ho was safe...
- Stop.

197
00:11:04,640 --> 00:11:05,770
Stop it. Just stop.

198
00:11:06,740 --> 00:11:07,740
I'm sorry.

199
00:11:08,570 --> 00:11:09,870
So please,

200
00:11:11,680 --> 00:11:13,040
just move on, Jun Ho.

201
00:11:28,630 --> 00:11:29,630
Oh Jang Mi.

202
00:11:31,530 --> 00:11:33,160
I will never give up on you.

203
00:11:34,770 --> 00:11:35,970
No matter what it takes,

204
00:11:37,640 --> 00:11:39,300
I'm going to make you mine.

205
00:11:52,620 --> 00:11:54,890
Where on earth is he?
He's not answering his phone either.

206
00:11:59,920 --> 00:12:00,930
Jun Ho.

207
00:12:02,130 --> 00:12:03,160
Jun Ho, what's gotten into you?

208
00:12:03,730 --> 00:12:05,960
Where have you been drinking?

209
00:12:06,160 --> 00:12:07,970
You know you're not supposed to drink.

210
00:12:09,170 --> 00:12:10,170
Get out.

211
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:13,140
I can't stand the sight of you,
so get out.

212
00:12:13,970 --> 00:12:16,340
Let's go. I'll get you a hotel room.

213
00:12:18,240 --> 00:12:19,310
You call yourself a mother?

214
00:12:20,310 --> 00:12:22,780
How can a monster like you be my mother?

215
00:12:25,180 --> 00:12:27,020
- Jun Ho.
- This is your fault.

216
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:29,690
The reason my wedding fell apart...

217
00:12:30,720 --> 00:12:32,360
is because of you.

218
00:12:33,760 --> 00:12:34,860
Why did you abandon me?

219
00:12:35,990 --> 00:12:37,860
If you were going to abandon me,
you should've never shown up.

220
00:12:39,430 --> 00:12:42,130
And if you were going to show up,
you could've at least been a good person.

221
00:12:45,300 --> 00:12:48,410
Why are you destroying my life like this?

222
00:12:56,610 --> 00:12:58,780
I'm so sorry, my son.

223
00:12:59,680 --> 00:13:00,990
I'm so, so sorry.

224
00:13:05,160 --> 00:13:06,360
I make you a promise.

225
00:13:07,490 --> 00:13:10,030
I'll make sure you reach the very top.

226
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:14,300
And I'll make sure you get
everything you desire.

227
00:13:28,180 --> 00:13:29,210
Seo Rin.

228
00:13:31,250 --> 00:13:32,250
Seo Rin?

229
00:13:33,180 --> 00:13:34,320
Where is she?

230
00:13:35,320 --> 00:13:37,090
Where did she run off to now?

231
00:13:50,070 --> 00:13:52,440
Goodness, Seo Rin.

232
00:13:53,100 --> 00:13:54,170
Are you feeling any better?

233
00:13:54,710 --> 00:13:57,610
You had Grandpa worried sick, you rascal.

234
00:13:58,240 --> 00:13:59,240
Grandfather.

235
00:14:00,580 --> 00:14:01,850
There's someone...

236
00:14:02,610 --> 00:14:04,650
I'd like you to meet.

237
00:14:05,850 --> 00:14:06,850
Someone to meet?

238
00:14:15,830 --> 00:14:16,890
Grandfather!

239
00:14:18,130 --> 00:14:19,130
And two are...

240
00:14:20,460 --> 00:14:24,000
Wait, no. What is going on?

241
00:14:24,300 --> 00:14:25,300
We're...

242
00:14:26,370 --> 00:14:27,500
twins.

243
00:14:28,370 --> 00:14:29,370
What?

244
00:14:29,910 --> 00:14:31,040
Twins?

245
00:14:31,680 --> 00:14:32,840
Grandfather!

246
00:14:38,820 --> 00:14:41,990
Now that the wedding is off,
I have no idea what's going to happen.

247
00:14:42,250 --> 00:14:43,290
Honestly...

248
00:14:52,160 --> 00:14:53,360
What now, CEO Chae?

249
00:14:53,730 --> 00:14:56,700
What could you possibly want,
calling me like this?

250
00:14:56,870 --> 00:14:59,240
Is Seo Rin home by any chance?

251
00:14:59,740 --> 00:15:02,770
It is her house. Why wouldn't she be here?

252
00:15:02,840 --> 00:15:04,640
Not Oh Jang Mi! I mean, Seo Rin!

253
00:15:04,710 --> 00:15:06,540
Gosh, this is confusing.

254
00:15:06,540 --> 00:15:08,580
No one's here, so don't worry.

255
00:15:08,650 --> 00:15:11,880
Anyway, don't let her in the house!
Got it?

256
00:15:16,420 --> 00:15:18,760
Unbelievable. Does she have no shame?

257
00:15:19,060 --> 00:15:22,430
Did she really just hang up on me
before I could finish?

258
00:15:22,930 --> 00:15:25,260
- Good grief. Seriously.
- Mom.

259
00:15:25,700 --> 00:15:27,160
Doesn't it sound like
someone's downstairs?

260
00:15:27,930 --> 00:15:29,000
What?

261
00:15:36,570 --> 00:15:38,980
Chairman, I know this is hard to believe,

262
00:15:39,640 --> 00:15:42,110
but Oh Jang Mi and Ma Seo Rin are twins.

263
00:15:43,450 --> 00:15:45,680
I can't believe my own eyes.

264
00:15:47,120 --> 00:15:48,250
How could I...

265
00:15:48,950 --> 00:15:51,120
have been so blind all this time?

266
00:15:52,020 --> 00:15:53,120
Hold her, Father.

267
00:15:53,760 --> 00:15:55,990
All right.

268
00:15:56,290 --> 00:15:59,230
Oh, you're so pretty. Oh, my sweet girl.

269
00:15:59,600 --> 00:16:01,500
It feels like my Dong Seok
has come back to me.

270
00:16:02,330 --> 00:16:04,230
CEO Chae only ever...

271
00:16:04,770 --> 00:16:06,800
brought me Seo Rin to hold.

272
00:16:07,710 --> 00:16:10,170
I'm Seo Rin, Grandfather! Ma Seo Rin.

273
00:16:10,210 --> 00:16:12,840
Yes, my sweet girl!

274
00:16:13,510 --> 00:16:15,810
What happened to your face?

275
00:16:17,510 --> 00:16:20,750
I was in a truck accident,
and I almost died.

276
00:16:20,880 --> 00:16:23,020
I was held captive this whole time,
unconscious

277
00:16:23,220 --> 00:16:25,220
I only just managed to escape.

278
00:16:26,420 --> 00:16:30,490
- Grandfather.
- Yes, my sweet girl.

279
00:16:30,960 --> 00:16:34,530
Your grandfather is so sorry.

280
00:16:34,670 --> 00:16:35,800
I'm so sorry.

281
00:16:36,530 --> 00:16:37,530
Grandfather.

282
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:41,370
The truth is, I'm Oh Jang Mi.

283
00:16:42,110 --> 00:16:44,440
I've been pretending to be Seo Rin,

284
00:16:45,140 --> 00:16:46,610
and I'm so sorry for deceiving you.

285
00:16:47,010 --> 00:16:51,120
I see. Yes, my sweet girl, come here.

286
00:16:53,280 --> 00:16:55,920
- Grandfather.
- There, there.

287
00:16:56,490 --> 00:16:57,960
Jang Mi. Yes.

288
00:16:58,360 --> 00:17:02,590
You were by my side this whole time,
and I never even knew, did I?

289
00:17:02,890 --> 00:17:03,890
I'm so sorry.

290
00:17:04,230 --> 00:17:07,200
- I'm sorry.
- No, Grandfather. It's okay.

291
00:17:08,030 --> 00:17:12,000
You'll need my help dealing with CEO Chae,
so I'll be on standby.

292
00:17:14,770 --> 00:17:15,770
But...

293
00:17:16,340 --> 00:17:20,410
what did you mean you escaped?

294
00:17:33,560 --> 00:17:34,560
Seo Rin.

295
00:17:34,860 --> 00:17:36,690
You really convinced the caregiver
to let you go?

296
00:17:36,890 --> 00:17:39,830
Yes. I told her
I'd give her a ton of money...

297
00:17:39,900 --> 00:17:41,430
to let me go.

298
00:17:41,570 --> 00:17:42,870
So just send the money already.

299
00:17:43,300 --> 00:17:44,370
You have the account number, right?

300
00:17:44,740 --> 00:17:47,670
I'll send it.
This is between me and Seo Rin.

301
00:17:47,840 --> 00:17:49,740
Okay, then I'll head to that address now.

302
00:17:50,070 --> 00:17:51,070
Be careful, Baek Ho.

303
00:17:52,580 --> 00:17:53,580
Just a second.

304
00:17:56,110 --> 00:17:57,110
I sent the money.

305
00:17:57,410 --> 00:17:59,780
Tell her she'll get the other half
after we get you out.

306
00:18:00,080 --> 00:18:03,290
Of course. Do you think I'm stupid?

307
00:18:03,950 --> 00:18:05,720
Baek Ho just left for there now.

308
00:18:06,060 --> 00:18:08,160
Okay, I'll be ready.

309
00:18:08,630 --> 00:18:09,660
Thank you, Seo Rin.

310
00:18:10,560 --> 00:18:11,900
I'm so thankful...

311
00:18:12,960 --> 00:18:14,430
you're healthy again.

312
00:18:20,200 --> 00:18:21,970
Here, have some of this
if you're getting tired.

313
00:18:22,840 --> 00:18:23,940
Thank you.

314
00:18:48,930 --> 00:18:50,230
(Kang Baek Ho: I'm almost there)

315
00:19:03,210 --> 00:19:04,210
Hurry.

316
00:19:15,130 --> 00:19:16,130
Jang Mi,

317
00:19:16,860 --> 00:19:18,760
it's time to make Chae Hwa Young pay.

318
00:19:22,370 --> 00:19:25,200
So that awful Chae Hwa Young...

319
00:19:25,200 --> 00:19:26,900
completely fooled me?

320
00:19:27,040 --> 00:19:28,310
Yes, Grandfather.

321
00:19:28,910 --> 00:19:31,940
Grandfather,
you probably know my mother too.

322
00:19:32,680 --> 00:19:34,780
- My mother's name is...
- Don't tell me...

323
00:19:35,310 --> 00:19:36,550
Jung Suk Hee...

324
00:19:37,250 --> 00:19:38,380
It's Jung Suk Hee, isn't it?

325
00:19:38,380 --> 00:19:40,350
Yes, that's her.

326
00:19:40,580 --> 00:19:43,150
(Bomdama)

327
00:19:46,820 --> 00:19:50,830
- She's the girl my son loved so much.
- Enjoy your meal.

328
00:19:50,890 --> 00:19:54,160
So that girl is the one who had twins.

329
00:19:54,500 --> 00:19:56,400
Yes, Grandfather, that's right.

330
00:19:57,170 --> 00:19:59,470
My mother gave birth to twins.

331
00:20:00,070 --> 00:20:01,310
But then CEO Chae...

332
00:20:01,640 --> 00:20:04,270
took Seo Rin away from my mother.

333
00:20:04,580 --> 00:20:06,710
No, she stole her.

334
00:20:07,110 --> 00:20:08,850
Mom!

335
00:20:09,610 --> 00:20:11,280
Mom!

336
00:20:44,380 --> 00:20:45,750
I can't believe this.

337
00:20:46,350 --> 00:20:48,420
To think she came to me,

338
00:20:48,420 --> 00:20:50,050
brazenly claiming
she was pregnant with Dong Seok's child.

339
00:20:50,690 --> 00:20:51,790
That wretched woman.

340
00:20:51,990 --> 00:20:53,760
I heard Chae Hwa Young...

341
00:20:54,120 --> 00:20:55,590
had a miscarriage
at the time she was pregnant.

342
00:21:01,570 --> 00:21:02,570
No,

343
00:21:03,600 --> 00:21:04,800
this can't be happening.

344
00:21:10,910 --> 00:21:12,440
You're asking me what you can do?

345
00:21:12,510 --> 00:21:14,110
To marry into the Dream family,
CEO Chae...

346
00:21:14,110 --> 00:21:16,210
- Just disappear!
- didn't need both twins.

347
00:21:16,280 --> 00:21:18,650
- That's the only way!
- She only needed one of us.

348
00:21:20,150 --> 00:21:21,520
That's why...

349
00:21:22,420 --> 00:21:24,490
she stole Seo Rin from our mother.

350
00:21:24,860 --> 00:21:27,520
She never told me she was having twins,

351
00:21:27,520 --> 00:21:29,130
so she only needed one of them.

352
00:21:29,660 --> 00:21:32,500
That's why she stole only Seo Rin
and passed her off as her own to me.

353
00:21:34,030 --> 00:21:36,000
That wretched Chae Hwa Young...

354
00:21:36,530 --> 00:21:38,270
fooled me completely.

355
00:21:38,540 --> 00:21:39,740
And that's not all.

356
00:21:40,200 --> 00:21:42,070
CEO Chae was afraid that
if she let my mother and me live,

357
00:21:42,640 --> 00:21:44,940
her lies would be exposed.

358
00:21:46,180 --> 00:21:47,880
So she tried to kill us.

359
00:21:48,650 --> 00:21:49,910
When my mother found out,

360
00:21:50,710 --> 00:21:51,850
she tried to save me...

361
00:22:03,330 --> 00:22:04,330
Now...

362
00:22:05,860 --> 00:22:07,900
she's regressed to the mental age
of a five-year-old.

363
00:22:08,930 --> 00:22:10,930
It's like my mother's life just stopped.

364
00:22:15,110 --> 00:22:16,110
That's terrible.

365
00:22:16,510 --> 00:22:18,840
Oh my goodness, my head is spinning.

366
00:22:19,740 --> 00:22:22,210
How can two people look so identical?

367
00:22:23,110 --> 00:22:25,180
Honey,
you can't get too worked up over this.

368
00:22:25,780 --> 00:22:28,620
Please, be careful not to collapse.

369
00:22:30,450 --> 00:22:34,420
Wait, so CEO Chae stole one of the twins?

370
00:22:34,990 --> 00:22:36,560
She didn't actually give birth to you?

371
00:22:36,660 --> 00:22:39,660
Our birth mother is a woman
named Jung Suk Hee.

372
00:22:40,730 --> 00:22:44,070
Grandfather, I even had a DNA test done
to confirm it.

373
00:22:44,900 --> 00:22:48,170
It turns out Chae Hwa Young and I
don't share a single drop of blood.

374
00:22:49,740 --> 00:22:50,970
On top of that,

375
00:22:50,970 --> 00:22:53,040
she had my adoptive father killed...

376
00:22:53,640 --> 00:22:56,080
because he knew her secret
about the twins.

377
00:22:56,410 --> 00:22:58,050
Oh my goodness.

378
00:22:58,120 --> 00:23:00,250
That's terrifying.

379
00:23:00,420 --> 00:23:03,390
Then, who was the person who confessed
to murdering Oh Bok Gil?

380
00:23:03,520 --> 00:23:05,320
He was one of Lee Kang Hyuk's men.

381
00:23:06,090 --> 00:23:08,020
But he ended up dying in jail, too.

382
00:23:11,230 --> 00:23:14,400
Since Seo Rin knows the whole story now,

383
00:23:15,130 --> 00:23:16,370
tell your mother...

384
00:23:17,200 --> 00:23:21,370
No.
Tell CEO Chae to get in here right now.

385
00:23:22,310 --> 00:23:23,370
Right now!

386
00:23:23,970 --> 00:23:25,280
That wretched woman...

387
00:23:26,010 --> 00:23:27,210
How dare she lie to me?

388
00:23:34,080 --> 00:23:36,420
Shit, I swear it was right here.

389
00:23:36,420 --> 00:23:37,620
What was?

390
00:23:38,290 --> 00:23:42,460
You didn't take or throw away the lipstick
that was here, did you?

391
00:23:42,560 --> 00:23:45,300
No. Why? Was it something important?

392
00:23:45,700 --> 00:23:49,500
Shit, where did it go?
Everything's in that lipstick.

393
00:23:52,700 --> 00:23:53,770
(DNA Test Result Report)

394
00:23:53,840 --> 00:23:54,870
(Ma Seo Rin, Chae Hwa Young)

395
00:23:54,940 --> 00:23:57,140
(Probability of maternal relationship
is determined to be 0.000054 percent.)

396
00:23:59,280 --> 00:24:00,880
(DNA Test Result Report)

397
00:24:01,110 --> 00:24:02,150
(Copying to USB)

398
00:24:04,580 --> 00:24:05,750
(100 percent complete)

399
00:24:05,820 --> 00:24:09,120
(DNA Test Result Report,
Conversation Recording Files)

400
00:24:12,290 --> 00:24:14,590
This is my insurance policy, just in case.

401
00:24:15,690 --> 00:24:16,890
Insurance for just in case.

402
00:24:20,130 --> 00:24:21,530
What are you talking about?

403
00:24:22,630 --> 00:24:23,800
The evidence you were talking about?

404
00:24:24,570 --> 00:24:25,800
Is the lipstick the evidence?

405
00:24:25,870 --> 00:24:28,610
Yes, it was a USB with all the files!

406
00:24:29,940 --> 00:24:31,840
So where did it go?

407
00:24:32,080 --> 00:24:34,910
Forget it. I have a backup plan.

408
00:24:35,650 --> 00:24:36,650
What is it?

409
00:24:39,750 --> 00:24:42,720
I hear you stooped to using Baek Ho's life
as a bargaining chip.

410
00:24:43,250 --> 00:24:44,860
Now that you've found Ma Seo Rin,

411
00:24:45,360 --> 00:24:47,090
what do you plan to do to Oh Jang Mi?

412
00:24:48,360 --> 00:24:50,660
- Jun Ho.
- If you try anything,

413
00:24:50,960 --> 00:24:52,730
I swear I won't stand for it this time.

414
00:24:53,360 --> 00:24:55,170
Don't you lay a finger on Jang Mi.

415
00:24:55,300 --> 00:24:57,400
I did it to give you Dream Group.

416
00:24:58,100 --> 00:25:01,070
If I combined my shares with Seo Rin's
and gave them all to you,

417
00:25:01,670 --> 00:25:03,740
you would become Dream Group's new owner.

418
00:25:03,740 --> 00:25:05,310
That was my dream for you.

419
00:25:05,780 --> 00:25:08,810
That's why I made up all those excuses
to rush the wedding.

420
00:25:09,680 --> 00:25:11,110
Can't you see how sincere I'm being?

421
00:25:13,220 --> 00:25:14,720
Since my wedding is off,

422
00:25:15,790 --> 00:25:17,690
I suppose your dream is shattered too.

423
00:25:18,590 --> 00:25:19,660
No.

424
00:25:20,020 --> 00:25:23,690
Ma Seo Rin woke up instead of Oh Jang Mi,
so nothing has to change.

425
00:25:23,860 --> 00:25:25,760
That's some interesting logic.

426
00:25:26,700 --> 00:25:28,930
It's the logic of a mother's love
for you, Jun Ho.

427
00:25:29,870 --> 00:25:31,970
Please, I need you
to understand my love for you.

428
00:25:33,870 --> 00:25:37,470
But right now, Seo Rin is missing,
and finding her is the top priority.

429
00:25:37,670 --> 00:25:39,280
Seo Rin is missing?

430
00:25:39,380 --> 00:25:42,550
Yes. Have you heard from her at all?

431
00:25:46,220 --> 00:25:47,420
Any news on Seo Rin?

432
00:25:47,720 --> 00:25:50,090
- Did you check Suk Hee's Side Dishes?
- She's not there either.

433
00:25:50,390 --> 00:25:53,060
I don't think she went
to see Oh Jang Mi, either.

434
00:25:53,660 --> 00:25:55,460
Then where on earth could she have gone?

435
00:25:56,230 --> 00:25:57,230
You don't think...

436
00:25:57,790 --> 00:25:59,200
she went to Chairman Ma, do you?

437
00:26:00,460 --> 00:26:01,630
That can't happen.

438
00:26:05,800 --> 00:26:06,800
(Suk Hee's Side Dishes)

439
00:26:10,440 --> 00:26:12,780
I should have investigated
more thoroughly back then.

440
00:26:13,840 --> 00:26:14,950
I apologize, Chairman.

441
00:26:17,610 --> 00:26:19,220
Where is CEO Chae?

442
00:26:21,620 --> 00:26:22,720
Where is she?

443
00:26:23,420 --> 00:26:24,750
Tell her to get in here now!

444
00:26:25,920 --> 00:26:27,920
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

445
00:26:33,130 --> 00:26:34,130
It's Secretary Kim.

446
00:26:39,900 --> 00:26:40,900
Yes, Secretary Kim.

447
00:26:41,540 --> 00:26:42,570
What's going on?

448
00:26:46,640 --> 00:26:47,680
Understood.

449
00:26:49,050 --> 00:26:50,150
What did Secretary Kim say?

450
00:26:50,850 --> 00:26:53,120
It looks like Seo Rin
went to see the Chairman.

451
00:26:53,750 --> 00:26:54,920
He's summoning you
to the office immediately.

452
00:26:55,590 --> 00:26:58,020
No! I told you that can't happen!

453
00:26:58,220 --> 00:27:00,120
Why couldn't you keep an eye on one girl?

454
00:27:05,560 --> 00:27:06,560
Unbelievable.

455
00:27:18,070 --> 00:27:19,710
Seo Rin.

456
00:27:20,680 --> 00:27:21,910
When did you get here?

457
00:27:22,510 --> 00:27:24,280
Hi, Mom.

458
00:27:25,820 --> 00:27:27,250
It's good to see you, honey.

459
00:27:28,020 --> 00:27:30,350
I was just on my way to get you.

460
00:27:30,850 --> 00:27:33,060
You should've come with me.
Why did you come all by yourself?

461
00:27:37,790 --> 00:27:38,800
Chae Hwa Young.

462
00:27:39,630 --> 00:27:40,660
Hello.

463
00:27:42,170 --> 00:27:43,200
Oh Jang Mi.

464
00:28:15,670 --> 00:28:17,270
(The First Man)

465
00:28:17,330 --> 00:28:19,500
I've had enough. Get out!

466
00:28:19,640 --> 00:28:21,700
Never set foot in this house again!

467
00:28:21,940 --> 00:28:24,140
Step down immediately as CEO!

468
00:28:24,510 --> 00:28:26,110
I could never bring myself
to ask about my dad...

469
00:28:26,110 --> 00:28:28,880
because it felt like I was accepting you
as my mother.

470
00:28:29,150 --> 00:28:30,710
I've always wanted to ask you.

471
00:28:30,850 --> 00:28:32,220
Who is my father?

472
00:28:32,520 --> 00:28:34,080
Ok Hee and Tok Hee are here.

473
00:28:35,220 --> 00:28:38,020
Ok Hee and Tok Hee are so cute.

474
00:28:42,130 --> 00:28:44,130
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
